negotiator.persistent

Interface StandardInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultStandardInfo

    public interface StandardInfo
extends java.io.Serializable
    Contains info about a previous session. Contains agents and profile played against, list of received actors that proposed bids and their utilities. Immutable. All components are also immutable.

    • Method Detail

      • getAgentProfiles

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getAgentProfiles()
        Returns:
        immutable map containing a set of pairs [agent, profile]. The order is as provided to the protocol.

      • getStartingAgent

        java.lang.String getStartingAgent()
        Returns:
        the starting agent: the agent that did the first action. With most protocols, this will be the same as the agent in the first tuple in getUtilities()

      • getUtilities

        java.util.List<Tuple<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double>> getUtilities()
        Returns:
        tuples [agent, utility] for all the ActionWithBids that were done, in that order (0 being the first action with a bid, etc). Agent is the party that did the action. Utility is the non-discounted utility of his offer. All utilities are in the utility space of the agent receiving this info.

      • getDeadline

        Deadline getDeadline()
        Returns:
        the deadline used for the session.

      • getAgreement

        Tuple<Bid,java.lang.Double> getAgreement()
        get the agreement. Returns null if no agreement was reached.
